{
  "uid": "lantern-dataplane-runtime",
  "title": "Lantern — Data Plane & Runtime",
  "tags": ["lantern", "ga"],
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "version": 1,
  "refresh": "30s",
  "time": {
    "from": "now-6h",
    "to": "now"
  },
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "name": "DS_PROMETHEUS",
        "label": "Prometheus",
        "type": "datasource",
        "query": "prometheus",
        "current": {},
        "hide": 0,
        "refresh": 1,
        "regex": "",
        "options": []
      }
    ]
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Active VMs",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 10,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "lineInterpolation": "linear",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "showPoints": "never"
          },
          "unit": "short",
          "min": 0
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "list",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "calcs": []
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "single",
          "sort": "none"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "lantern_scheduler_active_vms",
          "refId": "A",
          "legendFormat": "active VMs",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Registered nodes",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 10,
        "x": 10,
        "y": 0
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "lineInterpolation": "linear",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "showPoints": "never"
          },
          "unit": "short",
          "min": 0
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "list",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "calcs": []
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "single",
          "sort": "none"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "lantern_scheduler_nodes",
          "refId": "A",
          "legendFormat": "nodes",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Scheduler leader present",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 4,
        "x": 20,
        "y": 0
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "mappings": [
            { "type": "value", "options": { "0": { "text": "NO LEADER" } } }
          ],
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "red", "value": null },
              { "color": "green", "value": 1 }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": ["lastNotNull"],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "justifyMode": "auto",
        "orientation": "auto",
        "textMode": "auto"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(lantern_scheduler_is_leader)",
          "refId": "A",
          "legendFormat": "leaders",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Placement score p50 / p90",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 8
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "lineInterpolation": "linear",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "showPoints": "never"
          },
          "unit": "short"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "calcs": ["lastNotNull"]
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi",
          "sort": "desc"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.5, sum(rate(lantern_scheduler_placement_score_bucket[5m])) by (le))",
          "refId": "A",
          "legendFormat": "p50",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
          }
        },
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.9, sum(rate(lantern_scheduler_placement_score_bucket[5m])) by (le))",
          "refId": "B",
          "legendFormat": "p90",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Quota rejection rate",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 8
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "lineInterpolation": "linear",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "showPoints": "never"
          },
          "unit": "reqps",
          "min": 0
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "list",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "calcs": []
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "single",
          "sort": "none"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(rate(lantern_scheduler_schedule_total{result=\"quota\"}[5m]))",
          "refId": "A",
          "legendFormat": "quota rejections",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Data-plane heartbeat age",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 9,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 16
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "lineInterpolation": "linear",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "showPoints": "never",
            "thresholdsStyle": {
              "mode": "line"
            }
          },
          "unit": "s",
          "min": 0,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "red", "value": 120 }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "calcs": ["lastNotNull", "max"]
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi",
          "sort": "desc"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "lantern_data_plane_seconds_since_heartbeat",
          "refId": "A",
          "legendFormat": "{{data_plane_id}} ({{cloud}}/{{region}})",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "TODO — pending instrumentation",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 25
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### Not emitted yet — do not trust as live\n\nThe panels above are built **only** on metrics the runtime-scheduler and postgres_exporter actually export today. The following are **not yet instrumented**:\n\n- **Heartbeat-from-app metrics** — per-data-plane heartbeat is currently derived in postgres_exporter (`lantern_data_plane_seconds_since_heartbeat`). A direct push from the data-plane agent itself is not wired.\n- **runtime-manager (Rust) metrics** — the runtime-manager does **not** export Prometheus metrics yet (per-VM CPU/mem, isolation type, spawn latency, egress denials). These live only as **OTel traces** today.\n- `lantern_runs_completed_total` — run failure rate (OTel trace only).\n- `lantern_budget_denied_total` — runtime quota 402s beyond the scheduler `result=\"quota\"` counter (OTel trace only).\n\n_When the runtime-manager exposes a `/metrics` endpoint, add live VM-resource panels here._"
      }
    }
  ]
}
